<TD><B><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica"><FONT SIZE=+1>National Taxpayers Union
Unveils Campaign to Repeal Tax&nbsp;<BR>
to Fund E-Rate</FONT></FONT></B></TD>

<TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">The 300,000-member National Taxpayers
Union (NTU) has launched an Internet-based campaign aimed at stopping the
tax that funds the initiative to connect schools and libraries to the Internet.
Congressional leaders have criticized the program as a back-door tax imposed
without direct congressional consent. (<A HREF="http://biz.yahoo.com/prnews/980818/dc_ntu_web_1.html">YAHOO</A>)</FONT></TD>

