<TD><B><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica"><FONT SIZE=+1>Sun Microsystems, Lucent
Announce Pact to Integrate&nbsp;<BR>
Messaging Services</FONT></FONT></B></TD>

<TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">The networking software companies will
jointly develop software that integrates their respective ISP and communications
system software. The result: integrated voice, email, and fax services
on a wireless, worldwide basis. (<A HREF="http://www.wired.com/news/news/technology/story/14467.html">WIRED</A>)</FONT></TD>

