<TD><B><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica"><FONT SIZE=+1>Ericsson Unveils Snap-On
Wireless Data/Fax Modem</FONT></FONT></B></TD>

<TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">Ericsson says its DI 27 is the world's
first snap-on wireless data/fax infrared modem. It eliminates the need
to connect a traditional PC modem card and telephone line to a phone jack,
or using a cable to connect a mobile phone to a modem card. Weighing less
than half an ounce and half the size of a matchbox, Ericsson says it is
also the smallest modem available.&nbsp; (<A HREF="http://biz.yahoo.com/bw/980817/ericsson_2.html">YAHOO</A>)</FONT></TD>

<TD></TD>
