<TD><B><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica"><FONT SIZE=+1>CTIA Announces Educational
Tracks for WIRELESS I.T.</FONT></FONT></B></TD>

<TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">The conference and exhibition sponsored
by the Cellular Telecommunications Industry Association, will feature expert
moderators and panelists in educational tracks, geared to: professionals
in the areas of information technology (IT), information systems (IS),
corporate end users, wireless developers, advanced wireless, value added
resales (VARs), wireless integration, retailing, small office/home office
(SOHO), Internet service provision. (<A HREF="http://www.wow-com.com/results/professional/news/frameindex.cfm?articleid=3221">WOW-COM</A>)</FONT></TD>

