with Motorola for CDMA Buildout&nbsp;<BR>
in the Dominican Republic</FONT></FONT></B></TD>

<TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD>

<TD><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">Motorola's Cellular Infrastructure Group
(CIG) will provide CDMA (Code Division Multiple Access) technology and
equipment for Tricom's WLL (Wireless Local Loop) and PCS buildout plans
in the Dominican Republic. (<A HREF="http://biz.yahoo.com/prnews/980818/ny_tricom__1.html">YAHOO</A>)</FONT></TD>

